  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch31-01",
      "text": "Avril se cache dans le labo.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a cluttered underground steampunk laboratory, Avril crouches behind a brass workbench facing the viewer, one finger to her lips, Darwin pressed close beside her. A hidden trapdoor is prominent in the foreground. Medium shot, eye-level. Oil lamps cast warm amber light, tense and secretive mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "hiding",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-02",
      "text": "C'est le travail d'Avril.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "hiding",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-03",
      "text": "Darwin se cache aussi car la bande est dehors.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "hiding",
      "speaker": "Darwin"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-04",
      "text": "On a caché le labo parce que le monde va mal.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "hiding",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-05",
      "text": "Le monde reste dans la nuit.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "hiding",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-06",
      "text": "Une bande cherche les savants.",
      "imagePrompt": "On a smoky steampunk Paris street, a gang of three agents in dark coats and brass goggles stands facing the viewer, blocking the narrow alley. A conspicuous wanted poster is nailed to the wall beside them. Medium shot, eye-level. Gas streetlamps cut through coal smog, menacing mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "the_gang",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-07",
      "text": "La bande est une saleté.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "the_gang",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-08",
      "text": "La bande qui cherche les savants passe dans la nuit.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_gang",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-09",
      "text": "On a vu la bande, mais on se cache.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_gang",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-10",
      "text": "Il faut agir car la bande arrive.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_gang",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-11",
      "text": "Le travail a épuisé Avril.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril sits slumped at her workbench facing the viewer, eyes half-closed with exhaustion, Darwin nudging her limp hand. Scattered chemical vials and crumpled blueprints fill the desk. Medium shot, eye-level. A nearby oil lamp glows warmly, weary and drained mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "exhaustion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-12",
      "text": "On a privé les savants de tout.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "exhaustion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-13",
      "text": "La saleté reste parce qu'on prive les savants de tout.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "exhaustion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-14",
      "text": "Tout l'épuise.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "exhaustion",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-15",
      "text": "On prive le monde de la vie.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "exhaustion",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-16",
      "text": "Avril refuse de sortir.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground lab doorway, Avril stands facing the viewer with arms crossed defiantly, Darwin sitting at her feet. Heavy brass locks and iron gears seal the door behind her. Medium shot, eye-level. Oil lamps illuminate her resolute face, stubborn and determined mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-17",
      "text": "Il faut cacher le sérum.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-18",
      "text": "Elle a refusé.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-19",
      "text": "On a privé Avril.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-20",
      "text": "Il faut refuser car on a caché le sérum.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-21",
      "text": "Avril ne va pas sortir.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-22",
      "text": "Avril a une idée.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril faces the viewer with wide eyes and a bright smile, one hand raised as an idea strikes her, Darwin perking his ears beside her. A chalk diagram on the wall behind her is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Warm gaslight reflects off brass instruments, hopeful and inspired mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "an_idea",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-23",
      "text": "La saleté épuise le monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "an_idea",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-24",
      "text": "L'idée qu'Avril a est bonne.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "an_idea",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-25",
      "text": "L'idée va sauver le monde si le travail continue.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "an_idea",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch31-26",
      "text": "Il faut cacher l'idée parce que la bande cherche le sérum.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "an_idea",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
